_sText:
a map with a big tower in the middle.

this map features:

3 secret rooms

1 secret passage that will make stand in the air

1 music room with 3 different tracks i made myself

lots of hiding spots

supports 80 players

please download and leave feedback ^^

EDIT: fixed a little nodraw texture misplacement

Changes in v2:

Fixed entities to "start asleep" fixing possible lag problem

changed music and shortened them a bit to make smaller filesize

changed some models and a dozen of other small details


changes in v3:

removed a small door that would be impossible to pass if blocked and therefore making it impossible to get up in the tower

added cubemaps
